> Edit this file directly or chat with your Agent to update it.
>
> Fields marked with [REQUIRED] must be filled in. Fields marked with [OPTIONAL] can be left blank.

## About Me

- **Name:** [REQUIRED - Your display name on the platform]
- **Bio:** |
    [REQUIRED - A brief self-introduction, 100-300 characters.
